\c 142
\s Munyengetero womunhu anotambudzwa navavengi vake
\d Rwiyo rweMashiri rwaDhavhidhi, panguva yaakanga ari mubako; munyengetero.
\s Ndinodanidzira nezwi
\s rangu kuna Jehovha;
\s Nezwi rangu ndinonyengetera kuna Jehovha.
\p
\v 2 Ndinodurura kuchema kwangu pamberi pake;
\s Ndinomuzivisa kutambudzika kwangu.
\p
\v 3 Panguva yokumanikidzwa kwomweya wangu
\s mukati mangu, makaziva nzira yangu.
\s Panzira yandinofamba nayo vakandivanzira musungo.
\p
\v 4 Tarirai kurudyi rwangu, muone; nokuti hakuna munhu anondiziva; Ndashaiwa utiziro; hakuna munhu ane hanya nomweya wangu.
\p
\v 5 Ndakadanidzira kwamuri, Jehovha; Ndakati, "Ndimi utiziro hwangu, Nomugove wangu panyika
\s yavapenyu."
\p
\v 6 Teererai kudanidzira kwangu; nokuti ndinoshaiwa simba kwazvo;
\s Ndirwirei panavanonditambudza; nokuti vanondikurira nesimba.
\p
\v 7 Budisai mweya wangu patorongo, kuti ndivonge zita renyu; Vakarurama vachandipoteredza;
\s Nokuti muchandiitira zvakanaka kwazvo.
